  "text": "Due to a form of the joint itself and the course of forming, the self piercing riveting process may be considered using the two-dimensional axisymmetric model -the axisymmetric state of stress and strains [CITATION_1] . The boundary conditions have been defined based on the SPR riveting (Fig. 1) .",
